src:
Györ - Krim Mercator 31:26 (13:13)

02 Nov 2019, 17:25


Gyoer, 2. novembra - Rokometašice Krima Mercatorja so v 4. krogu lige prvakinj v gosteh izgubile proti evropskemu prvaku Györu s 26:31 (13:13). Izbranke Uroša Bregarja bodo v 5. krogu prihodnjo nedeljo gostovale pri Baniku Mostu.
text:
Györ - Crimea Mercator 31:26 (13:13)

02 Nov 2019, 16:25


Gyoer, November 2 - Crimea Mercator handball players lost to European champion Györ in 26th round (13:13) in the 4th round of the Champions League. Uros Bregar's selections will be hosted at Banik Most next Sunday in Round 5.
